---
// src/pages/about.astro
layout: "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
title: "About"
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen w-full text-white bg-black overflow-hidden font-serif">
  <!-- Background Image -->
  <img src="/images/about-hero.png" alt="Mystical Forest" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0" />

  <!-- Overlay Gradient and Blur -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/70 via-purple-900/60 to-black/80 z-10 backdrop-blur-sm"></div>

  <!-- Starfield Layer -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-20 pointer-events-none starfield"></div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative z-30 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-28 text-center space-y-8 animate-fade-in-up">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-pink-200 drop-shadow-glow">
      ✧ About <span class="text-yellow-100">Fishnini</span> ✧
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-violet-200 drop-shadow">
      You didn’t stumble here by accident — you were *called*.  
      Fishnini is not a fairytale you outgrow.  
      It’s a world you’re reborn into, where your soul remembers who you are.
    </p>
    <p class="text-md md:text-lg text-purple-300 italic max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Here, foxes whisper secrets of the stars,  
      and every glowing path leads deeper into your imagination.
    </p>
    <div class="pt-6">
      <a href="/stories" class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-pink-500/80 hover:bg-pink-400 text-white rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-pink-400 transition-all duration-300">
        ✧ Discover Our Stories ✧
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
